<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Account Locked</h1>
        <p>Hello <%= @resource.email %>,</p>

        <p>Your account has been locked due to an excessive number of unsuccessful sign-in attempts. For your security, we have temporarily suspended access to your account.</p>

        <p>To unlock your account, please click the link below:</p>

        <p><%= link_to 'Unlock my account', unlock_url(@resource, unlock_token: @token) %></p>

        <p>If you did not attempt to sign in or believe this lock was made in error, please contact our support team for assistance.</p>

        <p>Be Well,<br>
        M&D Realtor Services</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
